OL,3,CMichelle: NI Secretary has an 'ostrich
OL,4,Cmentality' over border poll
OL,6,FFirst Minister Michelle O'Neill has
OL,7,Faccused the Northern Ireland Secretary
OL,8,Fof State of having an 'ostrich
OL,9,Fmentality' about calling a border poll.
OL,11,FOn an appearance on Good Morning
OL,12,FBritain, she said that her appointment
OL,13,Fwas a sign of "the change that is
OL,14,Fhappening across the island".
