OL,3,CMichelle: NI Secretary has an 'ostrich
OL,4,Cmentality' over border poll
OL,6,F"The North was built in such a way
OL,7,Fthat someone from my background was
OL,8,Fnever supposed to be in the position
OL,9,Fof first minister.
OL,11,F"All the old certainties of the past,
OL,12,Fof that state that they were born
OL,13,Finto, are gone.
OL,15,F"I think my appointment does reflect
OL,16,Fthe change that's happening."
OL,18,FMichelle O'Neill said that she
OL,19,Fbelieves conversations around
OL,20,Fconstitutional change can be done, "in
OL,21,Fa mature way".
