OL,3,CMichelle: NI Secretary has an 'ostrich
OL,4,Cmentality' over border poll
OL,6,F"I think with Chris Heaton-Harris,
OL,7,Fwith all due respect, that's a bit of
OL,8,Fan ostrich mentality; sticking your
OL,9,Fhead in the sand and refusing to see
OL,10,Fwhat's actually happening all around
OL,11,Fyou.
OL,13,F"I said in my acceptance speech, let's
OL,14,Fmove forward together, let's walk this
OL,15,Ftwo-way street.
OL,17,F"Let's have power sharing working,
OL,18,Flet's make it work. Let's show the
OL,19,Fpublic that we have their backs when
OL,20,Fit comes to the day to day issues.
